text: Gao Heng (高恆; 570–577) was an emperor of the Northern Qi dynasty of China. Gao Heng is also the name of: *Gao Heng (philologist) (高亨; 1900–1986), philologist and palaeographer *Gao Heng (legal scholar) (高恒; 1930–2019), legal scholar and historian ==See also== *Gao Hong
title: Gao Heng (disambiguation)
